@PrivateHurrah wrote:

I have been interested in making a server for me and a friend to play alone without other people. I have successfully made a 679 Runescape private server with hamachi but it was pretty ugly such as the spawn point being in the cave goblin’s underground city, missing npcs, and others obvious problems such as extremely fast leveling up. I would rather make a more up-to-date server. That is when I came across this. I have downloaded the Renegadepkz source and client(v3.1) as well as the Rune-Evo cache. I am having multiple issues trying to set it up with no luck. Mostly the client gets the an connect error or it launches a form of Runescape 300. If someone could please make a detailed tutorial here either video or in text form it would greatly help me learn to make a private server instead of leeching from sources one day as I do plan in heading into a programming career path. If someone does respond to this request, you deserve a lot of kudos and thanks. Thank you.
